#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php
msgid "Omoikane Simple Sales Reports for Welcart"
msgstr "かんたん売上報告書 for Welcart"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php
msgid "https://github.com/omoikane-works/omoikane-simple-sales-reports"
msgstr "https://github.com/omoikane-works/omoikane-simple-sales-reports"

#. Description of the plugin
#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php
msgid "Create simple sales reports for Welcart stores."
msgstr "Welcart の売上報告書をかんたんに作成できるプラグインです。"

#. Author of the plugin
#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php
msgid "Omoikane Works"
msgstr "オモイカネ ワークス"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php
msgid "https://github.com/omoikane-works"
msgstr "https://github.com/omoikane-works"

#. translators: 1: required PHP version, 2: current PHP version.
#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php:50
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Omoikane Simple Sales Reports for Welcart requires PHP version %1$s or later. Your "
"current PHP version is %2$s."
msgstr ""
"かんたん売上報告書 for Welcart を利用するには PHP %1$s 以上が必要です。現在の PHP バー"
"ジョンは、%2$s です。"

#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php:71
msgid "Plugin activation failed."
msgstr "プラグインの有効化に失敗しました。"

#: omoikane-simple-sales-reports.php:110
msgid ""
"Required libraries for Omoikane Simple Sales Reports for Welcart were not found. Please "
"run composer install."
msgstr ""
"かんたん売上報告書 for Welcart の依存ライブラリが見つかりません。composer install を実行"
"してください。"

#: src/Activation.php:47
msgid "Omoikane Simple Sales Reports for Welcart requires PHP 8.2 or later."
msgstr "かんたん売上報告書 for Welcart を利用するには PHP 8.2 以上が必要です。"

#: src/Activation.php:58
msgid "Omoikane Simple Sales Reports for Welcart requires Welcart to be activated."
msgstr ""
"かんたん売上報告書 for Welcart を利用するには Welcart が有効化されている必要があります。"

#: src/Activation.php:67
msgid "Omoikane Simple Sales Reports for Welcart requires Welcart 2.11.10 or later."
msgstr "かんたん売上報告書 for Welcart を利用するには Welcart v2.11.10 以上が必要です。"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:168 src/Admin/AdminPage.php:169
msgid "Simple Reports"
msgstr "かんたん報告書"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:181 src/Admin/AdminPage.php:182 src/Admin/AdminPage.php:240
msgid "Sales Reports"
msgstr "売上報告書"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:233
msgid "You do not have permission to access this page."
msgstr "このページにアクセスする権限がありません。"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:322
msgid "Period"
msgstr "期間"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:325
msgid "This month"
msgstr "今月"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:330
msgid "Previous month"
msgstr "前月"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:335
msgid "Custom Period"
msgstr "期間指定"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:346
msgid "Show"
msgstr "表示"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:383
msgid "Template"
msgstr "テンプレート"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:445
msgid "Generate report"
msgstr "報告書生成"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:507
msgid "Print"
msgstr "印刷"

#: src/Admin/AdminPage.php:512
msgid ""
"If dates or URLs appear when saving as PDF, turn off \"Headers and footers\" in the "
"print dialog."
msgstr ""
"PDF保存時に日付やURLが表示される場合は、印刷ダイアログの「ヘッダーとフッター」をオフにし"
"てください。"

#. translators: 1: start date, 2: end date
#: src/Reports/ReportPeriodResolver.php:165
#, php-format
msgid "%1$s - %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s ～ %2$s"

#: src/Reports/ReportPeriodResolver.php:166 src/Reports/ReportPeriodResolver.php:167
msgid "F j, Y"
msgstr "Y年n月j日"

#. translators: %s: Sales support rate.
#: src/Reports/SalesReportBuilder.php:378
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The sales support fee is calculated by multiplying %s by the amount after applying "
"discounts to the product total, adding tax, and subtracting used points. Fractions are "
"rounded up."
msgstr ""
"販売支援料は「商品合計から値引きを反映し、消費税を加算後、使用ポイントを差し引いた金額」"
"に対して %s を乗じ、小数点以下を切り上げて算出しています。"

#: src/Reports/SalesReportBuilder.php:479
msgid "Canceled"
msgstr "キャンセル"

#: src/Reports/SalesReportBuilder.php:483
msgid "New Order"
msgstr "新規受付"

#: src/Reports/SalesReportBuilder.php:487
msgid "On Backorder"
msgstr "取り寄せ中"

#: src/Reports/SalesReportBuilder.php:491
msgid "Shipped"
msgstr "発送済み"

#: src/Reports/SalesReportRenderer.php:68
msgid "The sales report template was not found. Please reactivate the plugin."
msgstr "売上報告書テンプレートが見つかりません。プラグインを再有効化してください。"
